<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Application Received</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Application Received</h2>
        <p>Hello {{providerName}},</p>
        <p>A new application has been received for your job posting:</p>
        <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Applicant:</strong> {{seekerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Applied On:</strong> {{appliedDate}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>Please review the application and take appropriate action.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>WorkNow Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

